*************************************************************
******    Eclipse Shortcut and other eclipsy things    ******
*************************************************************
Add static import 	 		- Cmd + Shft + M
Remove unused imports 		- Cmd + Shft + O 	- To apply it on whole workspace you just have to select the project in the view Package Explorer and then use the key combination
Extract local variable 		- Cmd + Alt  + L
Assign a keyboard shortcut 	- Window > Preferences > General > Keys and searching for "Open Implementation"


How to remove STS Gradle and install Buildship. How to view hidden files in project/package explorer
	https://github.com/eclipse/buildship/wiki/Migration-guide-from-STS-Gradle-to-Buildship
	https://github.com/eclipse/buildship.wiki.git



















































































